reviews.review_text:
Immaculate Impeccable... ...Recording and performance from note one.

23 out of 5 Stars.

New Moon Friday the 13th! This show took me places I never returned from! This is a fabulous recording of this amazing show.  It captures the massive Phil bombs in CR&S...and the crowd reaction.  Very clean sounding AUD.  The Greek Theater was THE PLACE to see the Dead in the 80's!  The '83 run was the jewel of them all.

Rasta you are correct...

The big light in the sky was obviously just my hallucination...but it is still clear as the day it happened.  We saw it again while driving between Boise and SLC during the '83 Rocky MT tour.  No hallucinatory excuse that time.

This is how all Dead shows should end - no encore. as they put it all on the table during the show.
a NEW moon - Friday the 13th Show (not full, Google it) An excellent Audience source and show!

This has become one of my favorite AUDs... ...comes out at least once/month.

Feels like u r there, total clarity, good range, and inspired jams on every tune.
Fun - Great Listening to this makes me remember what I enjoyed so much about these shows.  Ripping China Cat.   Play it loud.

great stuff kick ass opener and great energy throughout despite bobs song selection  2nd set throwing up 10+ min and again and again closer... ouch!
china rider est/eyes killer!  fun nice aud tape better than mine... good sound. well yeah greek theater..
